{"tid":2056032,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"6.12 政府總部外非法集結　董事助理認罪判囚兩周","createTime":"2020-06-08T11:40:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-08T13:12:30.000Z","uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c13f1a48f96ad7bd2560982cfad4c6bf091a2a99","tid":2056032,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T11:40:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/6-12-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E7%B8%BD%E9%83%A8%E5%A4%96%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E9%9B%86%E7%B5%90-%E8%91%A3%E4%BA%8B%E5%8A%A9%E7%90%86%E8%AA%8D%E7%BD%AA%E5%88%A4%E5%9B%9A%E5%85%A9%E5%91%A8/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F6-12-%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E9%2583%25A8%25E5%25A4%2596%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%259B%2586%25E7%25B5%2590-%25E8%2591%25A3%25E4%25BA%258B%25E5%258A%25A9%25E7%2590%2586%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%259B%259A%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%2591%25A8%2F&d=N73AYdKZ8ITSJgwUZ5%2B19g%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=44c98bdc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F6-12-%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E9%2583%25A8%25E5%25A4%2596%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%259B%2586%25E7%25B5%2590-%25E8%2591%25A3%25E4%25BA%258B%25E5%258A%25A9%25E7%2590%2586%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%259B%259A%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%2591%25A8%2F&h=8ded5021\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/6-12-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E7%B8%BD%E9%83%A8%E5%A4%96%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E9%9B%86%E7%B5%90-%E8%91%A3%E4%BA%8B%E5%8A%A9%E7%90%86%E8%AA%8D%E7%BD%AA%E5%88%A4%E5%9B%9A%E5%85%A9%E5%91%A8/</a><br />\n<br />\n去年 6.12 金鐘衝突，一名貿易公司董事助理聲稱路經現場，搬動鐵馬，被控一項非法集結罪。他今（8 日）在東區裁判法院認罪，辯方求情指，被告當日受現場氣氛影響，有人叫搬鐵馬，被告移動一個鐵馬後，有催淚煙落在他腳邊他遂離開，並強調他當時並沒有戴口罩，亦無任何裝備，並非有預謀犯案。裁判官林子勤接納被告是路過，無證據證明被告與暴力示威者有直接關係，以三星期為量刑起點，認罪扣減後判囚兩周。"},{"pid":"72b2d4bcfb8920262744bf2f8729534949a5c6d5","tid":2056032,"uid":180168,"